## Description {#details}

Properties which a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinefunction">MachineFunction</a> may have at a given point in time.

Each of these has checking code in the MachineVerifier, and passes can require that a property be set.

Definition at line 137 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/machinefunction-h">MachineFunction.h</a>.
